title: Encentive.ambassador
author: Encentive.ambassador
content: Hey everyone, Encentive.io project is looking for assistance on 1) KOL/ Youtubers introduction - KOLs should have substantial followingRewards are determined by the number of the KOLs' followersConditions: KOLs are officially inducted and promote Encentive  for at least one month; invited ambassadors need to be in service; if conditions are not met, the ambassador rewards will be canceled.Class A. 100k+ Twitter followers Class B. 40k-100k Twitter followersClass C. 10k-40k Twitter followersClass D. 4k-10k Twitter followersBounty depends on the class/price etc 2) Business development 1. Recommendation of Projects to use Encentive.io services (commission paid if the recommendation leads to a deal)2. Project official cooperations Bounty will be commission - simple introduction of successful deal - at least 5% of the deal, deal closure by yourself - much more. More information about the project linktr.ee/Encentive_io If interested in either or both tasks, you can contact me at  jacob@encentive.io
